{"tid":1877593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣禁止口罩出口至4月底","createTime":"2020-02-13T06:07:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T06:36:14.000Z","uid":59971,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"317f5d6c7a3f0d52fe3a88ccf15bb145898fd540","tid":1877593,"uid":59971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T06:07:37.000Z","msg":"武漢爆發的新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情繼續蔓延，全球口罩供不應求。在台灣，經濟部表示，因應台灣民眾對口罩的需求，當局將會延長口罩出口禁令至4月底，政府徵用口罩的措施亦會同步延長到4月底。當局會視乎疫情檢討禁令，指如果疫情緩和，可能會提早解除措施。<br />\n台灣口罩出口禁令原先於23日終止。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%9B%A3%E6%B1%82%E3%80%91%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4%E8%87%B34%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95-207263\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E9%259B%25A3%25E6%25B1%2582%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25A6%2581%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E8%2587%25B34%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BA%2595-207263&d=2Od897eOL%2Byk6rGVR7zebSVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=1a989432\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%9B%A3%E6%B1%82%E3%80%91%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4%E8%87%B34%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95-207263</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣今次做得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4799a98a619b171bf250da72cf927f60c48bd00","tid":1877593,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T06:18:16.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"b85fcdd53db321b576c125d7d8c49e94d70a2835","tid":1877593,"uid":135404,"like":1,"dis